	   <tr><td colspan=2>While tooling down happily to go play with the Chief again, we butchered an amazing amount of Goblins (Still KoS to Sarnak grr) and just before we got to the 'city' this dropped. We were in a hurry, but I don't remember the victim being a Goblin Fanatic. We weren't near the pool either. Heading back down there soon for more Sarnak Faction and fun XP. General HT's in Chief area were 317 to 357 depending on the level of the SK, and with a good enchanter and hi MR (lots of casters down there) we held the entire chief area (clover leaf)with just 47 cleric, 45 Ench, 43 mage, and me 42 war. Most mobs have moderate HP's at best, and top out at 80's for Rok Gus. 14 kills and no Idol yet, but my Trollish self just LOVES that FR for those wizards. Singing Dagger dropped there too, but was told it dropped near the entrance before I got there.<br>Buddercup<br>Troll Warrior of Natural Sanction<br>Morell-Thule<br>&quot; Bad Gobbie! I make it go away now! &quot;<br>&nbsp;<br>Aeldwan the Enchanter<br>Wanderers of the Realm<br>Morell-Thule<br>"Doing the improbable daily to make the impossible look easy"</td></tr>
